    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[User info]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links>
          <link name="link0" internal="true" type="A">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/the-opencms-workplace/user-preferences-dialog/]]></target>
            <uuid>c90ae24f-d1cc-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </links>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The icon shows a user specific configurable picture. Clicking on the icon opens a menu providing access to the following options:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Upload user image</strong>. Upload a personal image that is shown for the user in the toolbar.</li>
<li><strong>Change password</strong>. Change the password for the current user.</li>
<li><strong>Preferences</strong>. Opens a <a href="%(link0)">dialog to edit the user's preferences</a>, e.g., workplace language, startup folder and more.</li>
<li><strong>Edit user</strong>. Edit the user information.</li>
<li><strong>Logout</strong>. Logout the user.</li>
</ul>]]></content>
      </Text>
